- [x] This steals the magic regular expressions that CTest uses to parse log files and addds them to Spack.  See here:

  https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/blob/master/Source/CTest/cmCTestBuildHandler.cxx

  These are BSD licensed, so the port is in `externa/ctest_log_parser.py`

- [x] We currently use these to do better filtering of errors from build output.  Plan is to use them to generate good CDash output.

@aprokop: this doesn't cause a regression on your error message from #5236, does it?
